 the top 10 titles, Cocomelon was the most watched title; it was on the daily top 10 for 428 days. The other titles on the top 10 chart are Ozark (85 days), Cobra Kai (81 days), Manifest (80 days), The Queen's Gambit (73 days), Outer Banks (72 days), Squid Game (66 days), Bridgerton (58 days), All American (58 days) and Lucifer (56 days).\n","* For category, TV shows had the highest number of days; they appeared for 4,446 days, followed by movies which had 2,611 days, stand-up comedy and concert/performance had the least number of days with 41 and 2 days respectively. However, movies had the highest number of titles; 354 titles, followed by TV shows which had 280 titles, stand-up comedy and concert/performance were the least watched categories with 6 and 1 title(s) respectively.\n","* The number of titles produced by Netflix is 406 while other companies produced a total of 235 titles.\n","* All American was one of the top 10 titles. It was on the daily top 10 for 58 days; one month in 2020 and three months in 2021. In April 2020, it was on the daily top 10 for 20 days. After April 2020, it appeared again on the daily top 10 on the last 4 days in July 2021, every day in August 2021 and the first three days in September 2021. I noticed this trend while exploring the dataset. It was also one of the top 10 titles.\n","\n","Interested in finding out more? Explore the [interactive dashboard](http://public.tableau.com/views/Netflix_16638770299160/Dashboard2?:language=en-US&:display_count=n&:origin=viz_share_link)."]}],"metadata":{"kernelspec":{"display_name":"R","language":"R","name":"ir"},"language_info":{"codemirror_mode":"r","file_extension":".r","mimetype":"text/x-r-source","name":"R","pygments_lexer":"r","version":"4.4.0"},"papermill":{"default_parameters":{},"duration":21.459803,"end_time":"2026-06-17T10:47:07.849674","environment_variables":{},"exception":null,"input_path":"__notebook__.ipynb","output_path":"__notebook__.ipynb","parameters":{},"start_time":"2026-06-17T10:46:46.389871","version":"2.6.0"}},"nbformat":4,"nbformat_minor":5}